ygData.subject: Re: [EQCheats] Blood Sabres
ygData.msgSnippet: Hiya, I checked into the faction you are trying to raise. Go to everlore.com and type in Busted Prayer Beads on the search. Click search and then click busted
ygData.messageBody:
Hiya,
I checked into the faction you are trying to raise. Go to everlore.com and
type in Busted Prayer Beads on the search. Click search and then click
busted prayer beads when you see it come up. Check the message board. The
first entry says how he got faction with the Blood Sabres. Thats all i could
find. Wish I could be more of a help. Do you have any secrets, cheats or
whatever that you could share with me? Thankyou in advance for any help you
can give me.

Kaino
